<br>
°Loot and Scoot. As soon as ghost loots the last item from the corpse, or the 3h are over that signal the end of clerical exp ress, a small dialog screen appears before the char users eyes, offering to which neighbouring zone she/he is willing to scoot to. On chosing, hes teleported to safe part of the wished zone immediate. The zone where he died non-exp death is closed for his entry for 1 hour. Of course, such LnS implementation can be abused to enhance Norrath travel times. So what?</font><P><BR> </FONT><P><font size=4 color="#000066"><u>Ulthien of the Shanks, VZ</u></font> <BR> <font size=3 color="#660000">Tribal Metilsmith Shaman</font><BR> <font size=2 color="#996633"><strong>(reincarnated agnostic rake)</strong></FONT><P><P><i><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#CCCCCC><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/umordier.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mordier</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered Patron</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>11/19/00</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>1:22:53 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Ghostform &amp; LnS</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I'd love to see it...but I have a firm feeling that Verant has completely turned its back on PvP.  <br>
